Adjoint sensitivity analysis following:
"Fast derivatives of likelihood functionals for ODE based models using adjoint-state method" https://arxiv.org/pdf/1606.04406.pdf
and
"FATODE: A library for forward, adjoint, and tangent linear integration of ODEs" http://www.mcs.anl.gov/~hongzh/papers/SISC_FATODE_final.pdf

that interfaces with the Stan Math library (https://arxiv.org/pdf/1509.07164.pdf, mc-stan.org)